{"tid":1366551,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[極重要!!] 暑期精選: 元朗國一日遊旅遊資訊","createTime":"2019-07-26T03:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T08:13:59.000Z","uid":278396,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f80c56896705b4397685800404d90d3a643c3cea","tid":1366551,"uid":278396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:46:50.000Z","msg":"話說我有個巴打係元朗人，佢見呢排大家對元朗旅遊都好有興趣，特別寫左篇旅遊資訊俾大家，方便大家外遊。<br />\n<br />\n巴打一盡地主之誼，希望能幫手振興元朗國旅遊業，各位巴絲不妨都睇下，認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想投資移民的話，元朗好似係一個不錯的選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n【元朗旅遊簽証事宜】<br />\n<br />\n今日收到一些關於入元朗是否需要簽証的查詢，我簡單回應一下：<br />\n<br />\n元朗鄉議局與特區政府簽訂「直入元朗」免簽証安排，所以大家入元朗旅遊毋須申請簽証。<br />\n<br />\n基本上元朗和市區的邊境是以大欖隊道作分界，所以市區人要偷渡入元朗的難度極高。自駕遊 (私家車)經大欖隧道入元朗須於關口支付 $48 的入境稅，不設八達通停車拍卡系統。建議大家選擇鐵道遊，購買 &lt;屯門 &ndash; 南昌 全日通&gt;，即日可往返市區及元朗無限次。<br />\n<br />\n元朗人重視傳統，大家仍可買到童年回憶的藤條。由於元朗盛夏較為炎熱，元朗人一般會穿白衣。元朗治安良好，居民自小習武，自組民兵，不設警隊。元朗自設河背水塘及稻田，居民過著自給自足的生活。<br />\n<br />\n元朗人的精神領袖是劉皇叔，曾經向外輸出「等埋發叔」的敬老精神，感動全球。<br />\n<br />\n貨幣：只接受港元及人民幣<br />\n電話卡：使用特區的電話卡，進入元朗邊境範圍或會短暫失去訊號，之後會自動啟動漫遊而不另收費<br />\n投資移民：經過盛夏之間發生的一場小風波，元朗樓價有輕微下跌跡象，正是投資移民良好時機。<br />\n紅燈區：我沒有相關資訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XEwUTK7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXEwUTK7.png&h=a6d8b344&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66872d8635dfdcb498370e1a446c607682767225","tid":1366551,"uid":2959,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:48:00.000Z","msg":"出埋閃閃書啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6BhRxi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6BhRxi.png&h=39b5e049&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc1fb96fed7156b9f78d934985a323b85c079a9d","tid":1366551,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:09:11.000Z","msg":"黎緊去元朗玩 請問邊到兌元朗幣最抵?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1366576\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1366576</a>"},{"pid":"75f661344aceeb66644e5d7fb2bc96d08c736e28","tid":1366551,"uid":13160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vq2EkGY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVq2EkGY.png&h=1618fd7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a9c0402c4f5dcc46de998dca840faba6396dce6","tid":1366551,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66872d8635dfdcb498370e1a446c607682767225","tid":1366551,"uid":2959,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:48:00.000Z","msg":"出埋閃閃書啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6BhRxi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6BhRxi.png&h=39b5e049&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:15:22.000Z","msg":"好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f0a94b66aabe9df3953222dccd9ddb573a5007","tid":1366551,"uid":2792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:27:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2780738f705c8542bfa1bec2ecff068d465d0fa7","tid":1366551,"uid":78186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:03:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d6d566e4fcb3ebb29d6c916f1fa27930cc013f8","tid":1366551,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:13:59.000Z","msg":"元朗特產呢？"}]}